children.html: Clickbaiting and whoring for visibility on social media at its best.

Notice also the ever present invitations to "like" or "comment" which are cleverly embedded into the content of the video. This is a well known trick that most "content creators" use on YouTube in order to push their audience into engaging with the video, therefore giving it more visibility with the YouTube algorithm.
